<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-TW">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>原原台聚</title>

<style>
body {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
    background: #f6efe7;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    min-height: 100vh;
}

.card {
    width: 520px;
    background: #fffaf5;
    border-radius: 25px;
    padding: 35px;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    position: relative;
}

.title {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 28px;
    color: #8b5e3c;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
}

/* 區塊 */
.block {
    background: #fff3eb;
    padding: 12px 16px;
    border-radius: 15px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: #6b4f3b;
}

/* 小標 */
.label {
    font-weight: bold;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
}

/* VIP */
.vip {
    position: relative;
    cursor: pointer;
}

.vip-detail {
    display: none;
    position: absolute;
    top: 30px;
    left: 0;
    background: #fff;
    padding: 8px 12px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    font-size: 13px;
}

.vip:hover .vip-detail {
    display: block;
}

/* 按鈕 */
.btn {
    display: block;
    margin: 20px auto;
    background: #ffd6d6;
    padding: 10px 20px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
}

/* 熊 */
.bear {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -10px;
    right: 10px;
    cursor: pointer;
}

.bear-face {
    width: 70px;
    height: 70px;
    background: #c89f7a;
    border-radius: 50%;
    position: relative;
}

.ear { width: 30px; height: 30px; background:#c89f7a; border-radius:50%; position:absolute;}
.ear.left {top:-10px; left:-5px;}
.ear.right {top:-10px; right:-5px;}

.eye {width:6px;height:6px;background:#4b3a2f;border-radius:50%;position:absolute;top:30px;}
.eye.left{left:20px;}
.eye.right{right:20px;}

.nose {width:10px;height:8px;background:#4b3a2f;border-radius:50%;position:absolute;top:40px;left:50%;transform:translateX(-50%);}

.blush {width:10px;height:6px;background:#f5b7b1;border-radius:50%;position:absolute;top:40px;}
.blush.left{left:10px;}
.blush.right{right:10px;}

.bubble {
    display:none;
    position:absolute;
    bottom:80px;
    right:0;
    background:#fff;
    padding:10px;
    border-radius:12px;
    font-size:13px;
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="card">

<div class="title">🎉 原原台聚 🎉</div>

<div class="block">
📅 5/9（六）｜🕒 15:00
</div>

<div class="block">
🍖 活動內容：燒肉 × 桌遊
</div>

<div class="block">
📍 台北市（報名成功後提供）
</div>

<div class="block">
⏰ 報名：即日起 ～ 4/30（額滿截止）
</div>

<div class="block">
💰 抖內 $520 ｜ 🎁 贈訂 ×10
</div>

<div class="block">
💸 熟人優惠(曾來過台聚者)：$120 ｜ 🎁 ×3
</div>

<div class="block vip">
💎 VIP 特權
<div class="vip-detail">
✨免報名費｜🚀優先權｜🎁大禮物
</div>
</div>

<div class="block">
👥 人數上限：15人
</div>

<div class="block">
⚠️ 不含餐費｜⏰ 遲到不等尼｜🍺 未成年禁酒
</div>

<button class="btn">🎀 我要報名</button>

<!-- 熊 -->
<div class="bear" onclick="toggleBubble()">
<div class="bubble" id="bubble">一起來玩嘛 🧸💕</div>
<div class="bear-face">
<div class="ear left"></div>
<div class="ear right"></div>
<div class="eye left"></div>
<div class="eye right"></div>
<div class="nose"></div>
<div class="blush left"></div>
<div class="blush right"></div>
</div>
</div>

</div>

<script>
function toggleBubble(){
let b=document.getElementById("bubble");
b.style.display=b.style.display==="block"?"none":"block";
}
</script>

</body>
</html>
